snippet.title: AMBER HEARD SHOULD BE FIRED. EMILIA CLARK SHOULD BE MERA IN AQUAMAN 2! SIGN THE PETITION!
snippet.description:
In this episode we discuss the recent rumors that Emilia Clark will be replacing Amber Heard in Aqua Man 2. We would love to hear your thoughts on this idea or if you have any other suggestions as to who should get the part.
 
Please SUBSCRIBE, LIKE & SHARE!

Petition To Have Amber Heard Removed From Aquaman 2: https://bit.ly/3dCKIyP
